The two ritualists who were arrested with some female body parts in a hotel where they had lodged by police have revealed how they lured their victims with money.

The names of the apprehended criminals are Ayodeji Saheed and Tunde Obadimeji who both confessed that more than 70 girls have been killed and their body parts sold to one Abefe Sadiq at #600:000:00 Six hundred thousand naira for one girl killed for him.
