When they were asked how they get their victims. They disclosed that
getting the girls was so easy.

“We lure them with money and fancy things.

They went further saying that girls of this days are easily lured with those things.

“All they need to do is to get or rent a fancy car with cash they would spend on the girls, and that is all this girls need. Then they are being taken to a hotel room where they are told that they would be having fun overnight but instead they are being slaughtered. reveal how they lured girls with money

The  two ritualists who were arrested with some female body parts in a hotel in Lagos  where they had lodged have revealed how they lured their victims with money.

The names of the apprehended criminals are Ayodeji Saheed and Tunde Obadimeji who both confessed that more than 70 girls have been killed and their body parts sold to one Abefe Sadiq at #600:000:00 Six hundred thousand naira  for one girl killed for him.

When they were asked how they get their victims. They disclosed that
getting the girls was so easy.

“We lure them with money and fancy things.

They went further saying that girls of this days are easily lured with those things.

“All they need to do is to get or rent a fancy car with cash they would spend on the girls, and that is all this girls need. Then they are being taken to a hotel room where they are told that they would be having fun overnight but instead they are being slaughtered.
